{"tid":2221494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢工業園區化工廠爆炸 至少5死1傷","createTime":"2020-09-28T11:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T18:00:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"593470f5816a541050e1733da7f695e91cd0bc7f","tid":2221494,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢下午有化工廠發生爆炸，事故造成至少5死1傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午約2時，在武漢天門市的岳口鎮譚湖工業園區，一個化工廠下午發生爆炸。事發後，涉事工廠內部瀰漫黃煙。一輛消防車及一輛救護車已到場，並停泊在工廠附近空地。兩名穿工作服及戴上黃色安全帽的工人及救援人員則在場以擔架抬出受傷人員。<br />\n<br />\n據內媒報道指，有目擊者表示，事故可能與洩漏硝酸有關。報道亦引述天門市應急管理局一名工作人員表示，事故目前導致至少5死1傷，傷者已被送往醫院，具體事故原因目前仍需進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/2b9942f0282e2b41693d98a5ddb5b512/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200928/_2020092818442913684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F2b9942f0282e2b41693d98a5ddb5b512%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200928%2F_2020092818442913684.jpg&h=ffb30eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd. stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1884725</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a18f41c10b5287dc769d3948d640b2d1a180772f","tid":2221494,"uid":61032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"維尼幫佢加完油冇耐就爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da073cba05416b126065a8541a1af103de5d0e8f","tid":2221494,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"Rest in peace <br />\n中國的會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6e147179d04bbe8cdf21c9620d135fc437211f","tid":2221494,"uid":144811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"今年真係支那大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"